<plot>Mylin, a young immigrant, comes to America with her Father in hopes of a better life. Instead, they are forced to work under a ruthless drug lord. Romance and the super natural come together in this tale of a young woman's journey to find herself. Her only refuge is a kind detective (Steven) from her past, who seems to be the only answer in the midst of all the corruption. Trying to piece together what he has in front of him, Steven discovers something that will change his life forever. Little does Mylin know, it will be her need for vengeance that will bring out all who are involved and stop all the madness that has plagued this small town. It takes a tragic turn of events for her to realize that to be complete, she must say goodbye to the person she loves.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?532953</url></doc>
